Summary: The Pipeline production visualization/automation system.
Name: pipeline-@CUSTOMER@
Version: @VERSION@
Release: @PROFILE_STAMP@
URL: http://www.temerity.us
License: Commercial
Vendor: Temerity Software, Inc
Group: Applications/Productivity
BuildRoot: @RPM_ROOT@/DEST/pipeline
AutoReq: no


%description
Pipeline consists of a suite of programs which use a high-level node 
based representation of the production process to perform a wide range 
of visualization, automation and administrative services.

The core features of Pipeline include: 
  + Graphical tools to visualize and control the production process.
  + Advanced revision control of production data files, processes and 
     dependencies.
  + Modeling of arbitrarily complex production pipelines.
  + Automatic generation of jobs needed to complete a production process.
  + Execution of jobs both locally and by a distributed execution queue.
  + Automation of data archiving and restoration.
  + Command-line based scripting of all functionality.
  + Rich Java based plugin API allowing almost unlimited customization 
     and extension.

